## FILE 4: `playbook_fluentbit_windows.yml` (mirrors `playbook_oneagent_windows.yml` exactly)

```yaml
---
- name: >
    Basic Fluent Bit installation using a package from Artifactory.
    Main node communicates with Windows hosts over WINRM.
  hosts: all
  remote_user: "{{ ansible_username }}"
  become_method: runas
  vars:
    ansible_connection: winrm
    ansible_port: 5986
    ansible_winrm_transport: credssp
    ansible_winrm_server_cert_validation: ignore
  tasks:
    - name: Import Fluent Bit role
      ansible.builtin.import_role:
        name: "./fluent-bit/roles/fluentbit"
```

