## FILE 6: Config Templates

**`fluent-bit/roles/fluentbit/templates/fluent-bit-linux.conf.j2`**
```ini
[SERVICE]
    Flush           5
    Log_Level       info
    Daemon          off
    Parsers_File    /etc/fluent-bit/parsers.conf

[INPUT]
    Name            tail
    Tag             vm.applogs
    Path            /var/log/siem/*.log,/var/log/app/*.log
    DB              /var/lib/fluent-bit/tail_app.db
    Mem_Buf_Limit   10MB
    Skip_Long_Lines On

[INPUT]
    Name            systemd
    Tag             vm.syslog
    DB              /var/lib/fluent-bit/systemd.db

[FILTER]
    Name            record_modifier
    Match           *
    Record          source    azure-vm-linux
    Record          env       {{ infra_environment }}

[OUTPUT]
    Name            splunk
    Match           *
    Host            {{ splunk_hec_host }}
    Port            {{ splunk_hec_port }}
    Splunk_Token    {{ splunk_hec_token }}
    Splunk_Send_Raw On
    TLS             On
    TLS.Verify      Off
    compress        gzip
    Retry_Limit     5
```

**`fluent-bit/roles/fluentbit/templates/fluent-bit-windows.conf.j2`**
```ini
[SERVICE]
    Flush           5
    Log_Level       info
    Daemon          off

[INPUT]
    Name            winlog
    Tag             vm.winevents
    Channels        Security,System,Application
    Interval_Sec    5
    DB              C:\fluent-bit\winlog.db

[INPUT]
    Name            tail
    Tag             vm.filelogs
    Path            C:\logs\siem\*.log
    DB              C:\fluent-bit\tail.db
    Skip_Long_Lines On

[FILTER]
    Name            record_modifier
    Match           *
    Record          source    azure-vm-windows
    Record          env       {{ infra_environment }}

[OUTPUT]
    Name            splunk
    Match           *
    Host            {{ splunk_hec_host }}
    Port            {{ splunk_hec_port }}
    Splunk_Token    {{ splunk_hec_token }}
    Splunk_Send_Raw On
    TLS             On
    TLS.Verify      Off
    compress        gzip
    Retry_Limit     5
```

